criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Brain injury (All patients with brain injury, at risk of developing intracranial
             hypertension, requiring invasive intracranial pressure monitoring. );

          -  Patients requiring invasive ICP monitoring;

          -  Age > 18 yrs.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  inaccessible ultrasound window;

          -  decompressive craniotomy before ICP placement.
